'''天主教莫拉芒加教區'''（{{lang-la|Dioecesis Moramangana}}；{{lang-fr|Diocèse de Moramanga}}）是[[馬達加斯加|馬達加斯加]]一個[[羅馬天主教|羅馬天主教]]教區，屬[[天主教圖阿馬西納總教區|圖阿馬西納總教區]]。

教區成立於2006年5月13日，<ref>{{cite web |title=MORAMANGANA* |url=https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20060513_moramangana.html |publisher=Libreria Editrice Vaticana |accessdate=2019-08-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824155043/https://w2.vatican.va/content/benedict-xvi/la/apost_constitutions/documents/hf_ben-xvi_apc_20060513_moramangana.html |archivedate=2019-08-24 |language=la |date=2006-05-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年有教友180,100人（佔轄區總人口38.7%）、九個堂區、廿三名司鐸。現任教區主教為{{link-it|羅薩廖·薩羅·韋拉|Rosario Saro Vella}}<ref>{{cite press release |title=Resignations and Appointments, 08.07.2019 |url=https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/08/190708a.html |publisher=Holy See Press Office |accessdate=2019-08-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190824151512/https://press.vatican.va/content/salastampa/en/bollettino/pubblico/2019/07/08/190708a.html |archivedate=2019-08-24 |language=en |date=2019-07-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

